      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 15:14:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Newsom说，加利福尼亚寻求贸易盟友的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/newsom-says-california-ready-to-talk-with-trading-partners-m92wcdw0</link>
      <description><![CDATA[州长加文·纽瑟姆（Gavin Newsom）表示，他正在寻求对加利福尼亚制造产品的报复性关税的豁免，并希望与全球盟友就新的贸易关系进行谈判，这使该州成为反对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的大量关税计划的后果的缓冲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/newsom-says-california-ready-to-talk-with-trading-partners-m92wcdw0</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 14:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非企业要求拉马福萨拯救统治联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/business-asks-ramaphosa-to-save-south-african-coalition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非商业领袖已写信给该国两个最大政党的领导人，恳请他们解决差异，并保持统治联盟完好无损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/business-asks-ramaphosa-to-save-south-african-coalition</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 14:43:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普打入中国关税报复，说政策将继续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-says-policies-will-never-change-amid-tariff-fallout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统抨击了中国（China）对他的全面关税计划进行报复，并誓言他的经济政策“永远不会改变”，因为贸易战的前景对全球经济造成了更大的破坏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-says-policies-will-never-change-amid-tariff-fallout</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 12:57:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非警惕对我们征收互惠贸易关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/south-africa-wary-of-imposing-reciprocal-trade-tariffs-on-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非政府表示，在华盛顿以惩罚性指控袭击美国后，急于对美国进口的互惠关税征收互惠关税将是不良的和适得其反的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/south-africa-wary-of-imposing-reciprocal-trade-tariffs-on-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 10:36:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈佛命令结束DEI，作为特朗普资助最后通票的一部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/harvard-told-to-end-dei-and-ban-masks-as-funding-threat-detailed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府正在对哈佛大学施加压力，其中包括消除多样性，公平和包容性计划的要求，这是在威胁要结束多达90亿美元为学校的联邦资金的几天之后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/harvard-told-to-end-dei-and-ban-masks-as-funding-threat-detailed</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 03:30:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，越南愿意消除对美国商品的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/vietnam-asks-us-to-postpone-tariff-and-engage-in-negotiations-m923qrv7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，林的越南领导人愿意取消关税，以免惩罚对东南亚国家进口的新美国职责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/vietnam-asks-us-to-postpone-tariff-and-engage-in-negotiations-m923qrv7</guid>
